Sept 7-10th @thecolormorale will be playing @blueridgerockfest at Virginia International Raceway. We will be joining over 150 bands for a 4 day festival that you are sure to remember for the rest of your life. We wanted this return to be something very special, and Blue Ridge Rock Festival gave us the platform to make it just that. Along with our full set, we will be playing a very special acoustic set to VIP members as well, more info will be found at https://blueridgerockfest.com. Follow them for updates along the way @blueridgerockfest and get your tickets now. 

We are also currently working on new songs, along with a new online merch store as we approach the 10 year anniversary of our Know Hope record. We told you this band could would never end. Sometimes artists need to catch their breath, so they can lose it all over again. 

Cheers to new life, and thank you for always being here.

Almost 6 years to this very date @thecolormorale played its last show. It felt amazing to get back up there with my brothers and rip a high energy set that felt like we never skipped a beat. THANK YOU ALL for taking time to watch our set at @sowhatmusicfest & thank you to @mikeziemer for giving us that opportunity!

📸: @dontshootskrlx

Life felt a little strange & foreign when I first moved to Las Vegas almost two years. It’s never easy making big life altering jumps cross country to start new chapters. It took damn near a year to find my footing and feel like a whole human being again with a lot of trail and error. With the introduction of @misskatiemariee into my life I finally felt I could start to begin building a strong, loving & companionate foundation that allowed me to wake up every morning and feel motivated to simply do life again. I quite literally feel like I won the lottery by getting the honor to call her my lovely lady.  We both are old enough and have been through enough up’s & downs in our lives that we just simply want to take everything we’ve learned so far and apply it to our relationship. I’ve never been with someone so emotionally in tune with their wants & needs and it motivates me to continuously try to better myself to be a stronger partner. Simply put. She’s an AMAZING human being and I can’t believe it’s already been a year! To many more. To growth. To love. ♥️
It was literally 114 degrees in Las Vegas yesterday. It’s hot out there…you best be finding a pool to jump in ⛱️
